name: Não olhe para trás, não é pra lá que você vai
description: Digital collage with nonlinear glyph which means "don't look back, you're not going there" in portuguese. (2480x3508px) Nonlinear glyph is a study I have been doing for 3 years about creating glyphs on a modular basis. you can find more information on instagram.com/valentim.ttt // Mateus Valentim, Designer and tattoo artist based in CWB/BR // twitter @vadevagarin
